@NODE Introduction
@TITLE "aiff.player · Introduction"


    @{b}Introduction@{ub}


    aiff.player is a player plugin for AmiNetRadio (@{" website " system "OpenURL http://anr.amigazeux.net/" })
    which adds support for Audio Interchange File Format (AIFF and AIFF-C)
    sample files.


    Following subformats are supported currently:

    * 8bit PCM mono/ stereo

    * 16bit PCM mono/ stereo

    * 24bit PCM mono/ stereo

    * 32bit PCM mono/ stereo


    * 12bit PCM mono/ stereo

    (other intermediate bit sizes should work too, but are untested.)


    * A-law 

    * µ-law 

    * 32bit IEEE Float

    * 64bit IEEE Float 

@ENDNODE

@NODE Requirements
@TITLE "aiff.player · Requirements"


    @{b}Requirements@{ub}


    - MorphOS 1.4.5 or better
    - AmiNetRadio 3.1 or better

